snippet.title: Iron Meat - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Iron Meat is a grind-house gunner featuring finger-blistering platforming ripped straight out of the 90’s from Russian developer Ivan Suvorov.

Like Iron Meat? Add it to your Steam wishlist!
